        <description>&lt;img src="https://mythicalprogrammer.github.io/p/php-howto-installing-pear-with-wamp-on-window/pear-6136656_1280.jpg" alt="Featured image of post PHP howto: Installing PEAR with WAMP on Window" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; This post was created awhile back on another platform and I migrated to my current one.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;installing-pear-on-wamp&#34;&gt;Installing PEAR on WAMP&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;step-by-step-guide&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Step-by-Step Guide&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-follow-this-tutorial&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Follow This Tutorial&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I followed &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://phphints.wordpress.com/2008/08/26/installing-pear-package-manager-on-wamp/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;this tutorial&lt;/a&gt; to install PEAR on WAMP.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;However, the tutorial &lt;strong&gt;misses the environment variables installation part&lt;/strong&gt; (it only covers Vista).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-setting-up-environment-variables&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Setting Up Environment Variables&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To set up environment variables on Windows, follow these steps (source: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://support.microsoft.com/kb/310519&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Microsoft&lt;/a&gt;):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Right-click &lt;strong&gt;My Computer&lt;/strong&gt;, then click &lt;strong&gt;Properties&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Click the &lt;strong&gt;Advanced&lt;/strong&gt; tab.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Environment Variables&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ðŸ“¸ &lt;em&gt;Example Screenshot:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;
