	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Environment Variables&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;3-editing-the-path-variable&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Editing the Path Variable&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Find the &lt;strong&gt;System variables&lt;/strong&gt; section and look for the &lt;code&gt;Path&lt;/code&gt; variable.&lt;br&gt;
Edit the &lt;code&gt;Path&lt;/code&gt; variable and add the following (separated by a semicolon):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;color:#93a1a1;background-color:#002b36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;
